Author: mentalox
Title: [ANN]Helbiz - P2P Transportation Rentals on the Blockchain. Presale Live!
Body: This is the car-sharing product.  A pilot is currently running in Hong Kong with a test fleet.  Unlike many other car-sharing services, the customer doesn‚Äôt actually need a key to access and start the vehicle.  Anyone wanting to participate as a supplier (someone who rents out their vehicle), is given an easy-to-install device to attach to their car.  This allows the customer to find the car they want, pay to rent, unlock, and start the car, all from the app. It‚Äôs seamless and negates the inconvenience of having to meet with the owner to obtain the keys.

Author: Farcical
Title: [ANN]Helbiz - P2P Transportation Rentals on the Blockchain. Presale Live!
Body: At first the project looked very good, until they decided to separate the companies with a scarce explanation, from that moment the token and the hbzcoin brand was at a total disadvantage, the team that formed it erased all interaction they had with the token and with the ICO in social networks, the new website of the token www.hbzcoin.com was empty, without team, white paper, roadmap, partners, and with only two exchanges.  In addition to this Helbiz promoted a swap of hbz tokens by bby tokens of a super fabulous project called Babylonia exchange, which was carried out in the initial phase and then also disappeared from social networks (the website still exists but only half works) .  The other brand that would be Helbiz obviously prospered, in fact they are about to launch an IPO in the United States and Italy at the same time, how did they do it after promoting an ICO and erasing evidence of their participation in it? We do not know, investors are very disappointed and alarmed.  The initial project that was to share cars with the phone disappeared completely from the Helbiz website (until last week there was the link and can still be accessed directly https://helbiz.com/HelbizCar), now they only focus on scooters and electric bikes. As for the token, you can still deposit hbz from a wallet in the app but the option to buy it with a credit card has also disappeared.   In addition, this topic link in etherscan was deleted, the reason in the official telegram group was asked and it was deleted without answering.

Author: Luca Helbiz Support
Title: [ANN]Helbiz - P2P Transportation Rentals on the Blockchain. Presale Live!
Body: A)Product:  The team is currently working on testing the Helbiz hardware to be installed in all cars on the platform. Significant amounts of testing are required to ensure functionality in all situations, it is not one single test but a series of tests. We are testing the device and lock mechanism in all circumstances, situations, weather, locations, models, cars, and will be carefully tested for reliability, durability, security, safety, synchronization and connection to servers, apps, cars and fleet management. We are dealing with the private property of our users and need to ensure everything has been carefully tested and optimized in worst case scenarios as well before allowing other users to unlock and drive the cars. Currently the initial testing is going according to plan and we expect the V1.0 to be released in the app store at the end of July. Simultaneously we are growing our partner network in Los Angeles currently on-boarding in-house and partner mechanics for the hardware installation to ensure a scaleable operation that can withstand high demand.  B)Buyback:  The Helbiz team is looking to purchase more than $1m (USD) of HBZ off the open market, to strengthen the company‚Äôs position both internally and to new investors . The Helbiz carsharing platform is set to be released to the public next month bringing incentivized organic demand to HBZ. The buy back of HBZ will be equivalent to more than $1m (ETH) and will be executed stage by stage. The team has executed the first stage of the buyback, buying HBZ equivalent to 400 ETH from its various exchanges between $0.01 and $0.04. The team will continue to acquire HBZ until after the launch with the intention of bringing the currency back to ICO price. The team will continue to buy back tokens for more than 1600 ETH over the next couple of weeks.  C)Token delivery:  ALL tokens from presale and ICO have now been delivered, no more investor deliveries will take place from the main Wallet and the circulating supply on CoinMarketCap does now match the actual circulating supply mentioned weeks ago.  Join the community Join us on Telegram: t.me/Helbiz Join us on Reddit: reddit.com/r/Helbizofficial/ Join us on Twitter: twitter.com/helbizofficial Join us on Facebook: facebook.com/helbizofficial/

Author: Luca Helbiz Support
Title: [ANN]Helbiz - P2P Transportation Rentals on the Blockchain. Presale Live!
Body: Bitlicense process started few weeks ago for the launching of HelbizPay. Helbiz‚Äôs US based company has, together with its US lawfirm, started the process of obtaining both the Money Transmitter License for all the states of America as well as the US BitLicense, allowing Helbiz and HelbizPay to:  ‚Ä¢ Receive virtual currency  ‚Ä¢ Transmit virtual currency between locations and individuals  ‚Ä¢ Store, hold, or maintain custody or control of virtual currency on behalf of other.  ‚Ä¢ Buy and sell virtual currency  ‚Ä¢ Control and administer a virtual currency  ‚Ä¢ Accept and receive electronic and wire transfers  By obtaining both licenses it will enable Helbiz to freely operate in the US allowing all US residents to acquire, send and pay with cryptocurrency directly from within the Helbiz & HelbizPay app, enabling our users to pay for both rentals and other services with Helbiz Coin. The licenses are an essential part of creating a seamless all-in-one platform with the ability to operate within, and integrate with, the current payment ecosystem in the US.  The process includes full governmental background checks of the entire leader- and ownership of Helbiz as well as audited financial statements of Helbiz and its subsidiaries in addition to various fees and money transmitter bonds.

Body: OFFICIAL EXCHANGE STATEMENT We are aware that a large part of the community only focus on exchanges, not realizing what creates long term value in a couple of months or several years down the line. We encourage everyone as investors to see the value of a growing platform and launched applications.    In regards to exchange listings: Helbiz will of course list on more than one top 5 exchange over time, and the team is in direct contact with several of the top 5 teams and have had in-person meetings with them, but understand that the Helbiz team‚Äôs focus right now is on launching the product and mobile applications.     Originally we had agreements with 2 separate top 5 exchanges. Our team decided to turn one of them down due to their activity behind the scenes since they are facing a large investigation in the near future which can impact their survival and the other top 5 exchange we had an agreement with is currently on standby as the exchange in question generally do not list coins trading below ICO price, especially if the project does not have a real world use case that has launched already. When HBZ is back at 0.15$ or the product has launched we will of course list here asap.  The team is of course talking to other exchanges, but currently the focus is on launching the two platforms and thereby bringing real world usage to HBZ allowing us to list on the top exchanges even if trading below ICO price.   The team has not forgotten any of its promises, and if you look back it has kept all of its promises but some with slight delays. Please note that it is our intention to list on all top 10 exchanges over time.     We encourage everyone to keep a positive tone and see the value of the work and deals being signed.

Author: Luca Helbiz Support
Title: [ANN]Helbiz - P2P Transportation Rentals on the Blockchain. Presale Live!
Body: First of all you have your right to post if you truly believe what you are writing, but the company nor the CEO have nothing to hide, but it is sad that you have made it your mission to try to work against an ambitious project that will help millions of people especially as we had answered your questions multiple times several days before.  Despite your intentions I will explain:  As mentioned in the Medium Article posted April 30th the actual circulating supply is 547m tokens, with the difference between actual circulating supply and CoinMarketCaps circulating supply being undelivered investor tokens (230m at 30April) that are blocked for various periods due to their individual contracts. CoinMarketCap is tracking the main wallet and is aware of this and updates it automatically every time an investor‚Äôs token is unlocked, we will be making multiple payments and investors are free to store their tokens where they want, on an exchange or MEW.  In regards to splitting up payments: All transfers from main wallet, including bounty and airdrop payments, have always been through one large payment that then has then been split up into multiple smaller transfers to the different individuals to minimize the amount of transactions directly from the main wallet, this is nothing new.  It was my mistake not to clarify that not the entire 30m was for an exchange listing in telegram, only a few million were for liquidity for a few different exchanges but the rest were deliveries to ICO & PreSale investors.  Of course all of this was already communicated through our news channels.

Author: noblex
Title: [ANN]Helbiz - P2P Transportation Rentals on the Blockchain. Presale Live!
Body: Hi, will Helbiz require me to own a fleet of vehicles to join, or could I basically rent my personal car or bycicle?  Also, will the service require to put back the car on the same location where it was taken, or it will be (like other Car Sharing systems in my country) possible to leave a vehicle wherever in the covered zone?  How will you implement the "open with your smartphone" feature to be easy applicable to every already existing vehicle?   Thanks

Author: cryptonikita
Title: [ANN]Helbiz - P2P Transportation Rentals on the Blockchain. Presale Live!
Body: Our mobility eco-system will soon provide access to individual vehicles as well as fleets and other transportation services.   Also, will the service require to put back the car on the same location where it was taken, or it will be (like other Car Sharing systems in my country) possible to leave a vehicle wherever in the covered zone? After finding a car and verifying your identity, you will have to accept the terms and conditions, such as the fare and duration of the rental, and purchase an insurance policy covering the trip, through an immutable intelligent contract. Each owner can set their own specific terms and conditions   How will you implement the "open with your smartphone" feature to be easy applicable to every already existing vehicle? This functionality will be available if the owner has enabled it. More information will follow.  Make sure to join the Helbiz Telegram group too to get all of your questions answered: https://t.me/helbiz
